---
import Layout from '../../Base.astro';
import SimpleHero from '../../components/SimpleHero.astro';
import FeaturedArticles from "../../components/FeaturedArticles.astro";
import ServicesRelatedWork from "../../components/ServicesRelatedWork.astro";
import "../../styles/pages/_services-list.scss";

---

<Layout
	title='Print Design | Florida Design Agency'
	description='Print still matters when people need something they can hold, reference, or take with them. We design print pieces that stay on brand, communicate fast, and hold up in production.'
>
	<SimpleHero tagline='Branding & Design Services' title='Print Design' description="Print still matters when people need something they can hold, reference, or take with them. We design print pieces that stay on brand, communicate fast, and hold up in production." lottieFile='print-design.json'/>
	<div class='service-body'>
		<div class='wrapper wrapper--narrow'>
			<h2>Where teams get stuck</h2>
			<p>
				Print pieces often get rushed from digital assets without thinking about format, hierarchy, or production. The result is material that feels off-brand, reads poorly, or creates extra problems when it reaches the printer.
			</p>
			<p>When someone picks up a brochure, poster, or sales piece, the message has to land quickly and still look intentional in the real world.</p>
			<h2>How we fix it</h2>
			<ul>
				<li>Magazine / newspaper Design</li>
				<li>Book Cover Design</li>
				<li>Brochures and Pamphlet Design</li>
				<li>Poster Design</li>
				<li>Event Collateral</li>
			</ul>
			<p>We design for the physical piece itself, considering readability, layout, sizing, and production details so the final result feels polished before it ever goes to print.</p>
			<h2>What moving forward looks like</h2>
			<p>If you need print materials for a launch, event, campaign, or sales team, we can shape the message, design the piece, and prepare files your printer can actually use without cleanup.</p>
			<p><a href='/contact/' class='button button--green'>Plan Your Print Piece</a></p>
		</div>
		<ServicesRelatedWork tag={71} />
	</div>
	<FeaturedArticles />
</Layout>
